data.description: If you are looking for a great floor-plan, this is the home for you. This 3 bedroom, 1.75 bath home has had many upgrades to include stainless appliances, a new refrigerated air system, a new furnace, a new water heater, and water softener. The living area of this home comes with a gorgeous fireplace, laminate flooring, and a nice large window for natural light.  With low maintenance front and backyard landscaping, good amounts of storage, and a great location, this will not last long. Call to view today.
